@prsunny It can be merged without https://github.com/sonic-net/sonic-buildimage/pull/12853. BGP facts and FIB test passed on T1-64-LAG with this change.

Please note, that I had to mark VS tests with ```xfail``` because they require VS changes done in https://github.com/sonic-net/sonic-buildimage/pull/12853. Otherwise, it is not possible to merge one without the other in order to not break tests or image.
Later this mark has to be removed once sonic-buildimage PR is merged.

@StormLiangMS @jcaiMR BGP suppress FIB pending test cases are already available in PRs - test plan + implementation:
- https://github.com/sonic-net/sonic-mgmt/pull/7475
- https://github.com/sonic-net/sonic-mgmt/pull/7430
